{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-163-cross-hatched-triangles","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 163: Linije koje se presecaju na krugu","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Zamislite ravnokraki trougao na kojem su povučene prave linije od svakog vrha do sredine nasuprotne stranice, kao što je prikazano u jedinici trouglu na dijagramu ispod.</p>\n<img alt=\"triangles with size 1 and size 2\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/cross-hatched-triangles.gif\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Sada se unutar tog trougla mogu videti šesnaest trouglova različitih oblika, veličina, pravaca ili lokacija. Korišćenjem trouglova veličine 1 kao građevinskih blokova, mogu se formirati veći trouglovi, kao što je trougao veličine 2 na gore prikazanom crtežu. Sto četiri trougla različitih oblika, veličina, pravaca ili lokacija sada se mogu videti u tom trouglu veličine 2.</p>\n<p>Očigledno je da trougao veličine 2 sadrži 4 trougla veličine 1. Trougao veličine 3 sadrži 9 trouglova veličine 1, a trougao veličine $n$ sadrži $n^2$ trouglova veličine 1.</p>\n<p>Ako označimo $T(n)$ kao broj trouglova koji postoje u trouglu veličine $n$, onda</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{align}\n&#x26; T(1) = 16 \\\\\n&#x26; T(2) = 104\n\\end{align}$$</p>\n<p>Pronađi $T(36)$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f40f1000cf542c50ff22","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301797,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-163-cross-hatched-triangles"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function crossHatchedTriangles() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\ncrossHatchedTriangles();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>crossHatchedTriangles()</code> treba da vrati <code>343047</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(crossHatchedTriangles(), 343047);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-101-to-200","dashedName":"problem-163-cross-hatched-triangles","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":true,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-164-numbers-for-which-no-three-consecutive-digits-have-a-sum-greater-than-a-given-value","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-162-hexadecimal-numbers","id":"5900f40f1000cf542c50ff22","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-163-cross-hatched-triangles"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}